\c 28
\s USolomoni ukhethwa ukuthi akhe ithempeli
\p
\v 1 UDavida wasebuthanisa zonke iziphathamandla zakoIsrayeli\x + 23.2.\x*, iziphathamandla zezizwe\x + 27.16-22.\x*, leziphathamandla zezigaba ezazisebenzela inkosi\x + 27.1-15.\x*, labaphathi bezinkulungwane, labaphathi bamakhulu, labaphathi bempahla yonke labezifuyo zenkosi labezamadodana ayo\x + 27.25-31.\x*, lezinduna, lamaqhawe, lawo wonke amaqhawe alamandla, eJerusalema\x + 11.10-47.\x*.
\v 2 UDavida inkosi wasesima ngenyawo zakhe wathi: Ngilalelani, bafowethu labantu bami. Mina, kwakusenhliziyweni yami ukwakhela umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* indlu yokuphumula\x + 22.7.\x*, leyisigcabha senyawo zikaNkulunkulu wethu, ngenza amalungiselelo okwakha\x + Hlab. 99.5. 132.7. Isa. 66.1. Lilo 2.1. Hlab. 110.1.\x*.
\v 3 Kodwa uNkulunkulu wathi kimi: Kawuyikulakhela ibizo lami indlu, ngoba wena ungumuntu wempi, uchithe igazi elinengi\x + 17.4. 2 Sam. 7.5,13. 1 Kho. 5.3-5.\x*.
\v 4 Kanti iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli yangikhetha kuyo yonke indlu kababa ukuthi ngibe yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli\x + 5.2. Gen. 49.8. Hlab. 78.67,68.\x* kuze kube nininini\x + 28.7,8. 17.23,27.\x*; ngoba yakhetha uJuda ukuba ngumbusi\x + 5.2. Gen. 49.8. Hlab. 78.67,68.\x*, lendlini yakoJuda indlu kababa\x + 1 Sam. 16.1.\x*; laphakathi kwamadodana kababa yangithanda uku\add ng\add*enza \add ngi\add*be yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli wonke\x + 1 Sam. 16.12,13.\x*.
\v 5 Lakuwo wonke amadodana ami (ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yanginika amadodana amanengi\x + 3.1-9. 14.3-7.\x*) yakhetha uSolomoni indodana yami\x + 22.9. 23.1.\x* ukuthi ahlale esihlalweni sobukhosi sombuso weN\nd kosi\nd* phezu kukaIsrayeli\x + 29.23. 1 Kho. 3.7.\x*.
\v 6 Yasisithi kimi: USolomoni indodana yakho nguye ozakwakha indlu yami lamaguma ami, ngoba ngimkhethile ukuba yindodana yami, lami ngizakuba nguyise\x + 17.12. 22.9,10. 2 Sam. 7.13,14. 1 Kho. 5.5. 2 Lan. 1.9.\x*.
\v 7 Njalo ngizawuqinisa umbuso wakhe kuze kube nininini\x + 28.7,8. 17.23,27.\x* uba eqina ukwenza imilayo yami lezahlulelo zami njengalamuhla\x + 22.13.\x*.
\v 8 Ngakho-ke phambi kwamehlo kaIsrayeli wonke, ibandla leN\nd kosi\nd*, lendlebeni zikaNkulunkulu wethu, gcinani lidinge yonke imilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, ukuze lidle ilifa lalelilizwe elihle, lenze abantwana benu badle ilifa \add lalo\add* emva kwenu kuze kube nininini\x + 28.7,8. 17.23,27.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Wena-ke, Solomoni ndodana yami, mazi uNkulunkulu kayihlo\x + Hlu. 2.10. Hos. 4.1.\x*, umkhonze ngenhliziyo epheleleyo langengqondo evumayo\x + 1 Kho. 8.61.\x*; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* iyazihlola zonke inhliziyo\x + 29.17. 1 Sam. 16.7. Hlab. 139.2. Zaga 17.3. Isam. 2.23.\x*, iqedisise konke ukuzindla kwemicabango. Uba uyidinga, izatholwa nguwe\x + 29.18. Gen. 6.5.\x*; kodwa uba uyitshiya\x + Josh. 24.20.\x*, izakulahla kokuphela\x + 2 Lan. 11.14. 29.19.\x*.
\v 10 Bona-ke, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ikukhethile ukuthi wakhe indlu ibe yindlu engcwele; qina, ukwenze\x + 28.20. Ezra 10.4.\x*.
\p
\v 11 UDavida wasenika uSolomoni indodana yakhe umdwebo\x + 28.19. Eks. 25.40.\x* wekhulusi\x + 1 Kho. 6.3. 2 Lan. 3.4.\x*, lowezindlu zalo, loweziphala zezinto eziligugu, lowamakamelo aphezulu\x + 2 Lan. 3.9. 1 Kho. 6.5.\x*, lowamakamelo aphakathi, lowendlu yesihlalo somusa\x + Eks. 25.17.\x*.
\v 12 Lomdwebo wakho konke ayelakho ngoMoya, lowamaguma endlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*, lowamakamelo wonke azingelezeleyo\x + 2 Kho. 23.11.\x*, loweziphala zezinto eziligugu zendlu kaNkulunkulu, loweziphala zokuligugu zezinto ezingcwele\x + 26.20.\x*,
\v 13 lowezigaba zabapristi\x + 24.1.\x* lezamaLevi\x + 23.6.\x*, lowomsebenzi wonke wenkonzo yendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*, lowezitsha zonke zenkonzo yendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 14 \add Wapha\add* igolide ngesisindo nge\add zinto ze\add*golide, ngempahla yonke yenkonzo ngenkonzo, ngempahla yonke yesiliva ngesisindo, ngempahla yonke yenkonzo ngenkonzo,
\v 15 lesisindo sezinti zesibane zegolide\x + Eks. 25.31.\x*, lezibane zazo zegolide\x + Eks. 25.37.\x*, ngesisindo soluthi lwesibane ngalunye lezibane zalo, langezinti zesibane zesiliva, ngesisindo soluthi lwesibane lezibane zalo, njengomsebenzi woluthi lwesibane ngalunye.
\v 16 \add Wa\add*se\add nika\add* igolide ngesisindo lamatafula ezinkwa zokubukiswa, ngalelo lalelotafula, lesiliva samatafula esiliva.
\v 17 Lamafologwe\x + Eks. 38.3. 1 Sam. 2.13,14. 2 Lan. 4.16.\x* lemiganu yokufafaza\x + Eks. 38.3.\x* lezinkezo\x + Eks. 25.29. Nani 4.7.\x* zegolide elicwengekileyo, langezitsha zegolide ngesisindo saleso lalesositsha\x + Ezra 1.10. 8.27.\x*, langezitsha zesiliva ngesisindo saleso lalesositsha.
\v 18 Langelathi lempepha\x + Eks. 30.1.\x* igolide elicwengekileyo ngesisindo\x + 29.4. Hlab. 12.6.\x*, langomdwebo wenqola \w yamakherubhi\w**\x + Eks. 25.18-22. 1 Sam. 4.4. 1 Kho. 6.23-28.\x* egolide elule \add impiko\x + Eks. 25.20. 1 Kho. 6.27.\x*\add* agubuzela umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 19 \add UDavida wathi:\add* Konke lokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* yenza \add ngi\add*kuqedisise ngombhalo\x + Eks. 18.4.\x* ngesandla \add sayo\add* phezu kwami\x + 28.11,12. Eks. 25.40.\x*, yonke imisebenzi yomdwebo.
\v 20 UDavida wasesithi kuSolomoni indodana yakhe: Qina, ube lesibindi, usebenze; ungesabi, ungatshaywa luvalo\x + 22.13.\x*; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu, uNkulunkulu wami, ilawe\x + Josh. 1.5.\x*. Kayisoze yakulahla, kayisoze yakutshiya, uze uqede umsebenzi wonke wenkonzo yendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 22.13.\x*.
\v 21 Khangela-ke, izigaba zabapristi lezamaLevi, zenkonzo yonke yendlu kaNkulunkulu\x + 28.13.\x*; njalo \add kuzakuba \add*lawe kuwo wonke umsebenzi, wonke oyingcitshi ovumayo kuyo yonke inkonzo, labaphathi labo bonke abantu \add bazakuba\add* njengokulaya kwakho konke\x + Eks. 35.25,26. 36.1,2.\x*.